w">Thất nguyệt 6 - 七月 6</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-7/poem-_Y_ZwtenVmhfHtsbT4YCdQ">Thất nguyệt 7 - 七月 7</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/Thi%C3%AAn-H%C6%B0ng-tr%E1%BA%A5n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zfk8LWGL0mEgBMai1LRNPA">Thiên Hưng trấn phú - 天興鎮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/author-UlfffDmWp64stOugtjh9rQ">Nguyễn Bá Thông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Thu%C3%BD-Hoa-s%C6%A1n/poem-JyokTsUCXU7xNWft5ka9IQ">Thuý Hoa sơn - 翠花山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%E1%BB%8B-ch%C6%B0-nhi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-_mr-qRBxrJRXds_c5ms_Qw">Xuân nhật thị chư nhi kỳ 1 - 春日示諸兒其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
